import React from 'react'
import {Unit} from "./UnitSelector/Unit"
import {UnitSelector} from "./UnitSelector/UnitSelector"

export const Defender = ({unit, setUnit, units}) => {
  const baseShields = units?.find(unit2 => unit?.name === unit2.name)?.base.shields
  const baseHealth = units?.find(unit2 => unit?.name === unit2.name)?.base.health

    return <UnitSelector setUnit={setUnit} currentUnit={unit} units={units}>
    </UnitSelector>
  }
